---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Section from '../components/Section.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About — CxRomos">
  <Section eyebrow="About" title="CxRomos is a founder-led software company focused on operational intelligence." description="The company is led by Danijel Kecman, a software engineer and systems builder with 20+ years across mobile, enterprise platforms, real-time systems, UX, cloud, and product architecture.">
    <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.04] p-8 text-slate-300 leading-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Why this company exists</h2>
        <p class="mt-4">Most operational software shows data. Very little of it helps teams make better decisions when the context is incomplete, moving quickly, and expensive to misread.</p>
        <p class="mt-4">CxRomos focuses on the layer between raw operational data and human judgment: routing logic, event systems, AI-assisted interpretation, and interfaces that compress complexity.</p>
        <p class="mt-4">The underlying belief is simple: automation starts in the mind, not the machine. Software only amplifies the thinking behind it — so the work begins by making the decision logic explicit, then building systems that extend it.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.04] p-8 text-slate-300 leading-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Founder profile</h2>
        <p class="mt-4">Danijel’s background spans mobile engineering, real-time platforms, cloud infrastructure, enterprise applications, system design, and product strategy.</p>
        <p class="mt-4">The current focus is aviation, geospatial routing, AI-native operational workflows, and decision infrastructure for complex systems.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>
</BaseLayout>
